      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Queue / Score Comparison\nThis dashboard compares the NMT fast path and LLM heavy path side by side.\n\nAll **Approx** series use current `telephon` timing summaries and must be interpreted as operational approximations, not formula-grade measurements. `approx_score_nmt_seconds` and `approx_score_llm_seconds` are unweighted base scores only; the router still applies per-request `w_fast = 1 + alpha * p_llm` and `w_heavy = 1 + alpha * (1 - p_llm)` before choosing the smaller weighted score.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "About This Dashboard",
      "type": "text"
    },
